rth flagging because it almost shipped invisible work.\n- `benchmarks/graph/scripts/providers.py` had an uncommitted change from before this task started (`codex: gpt-5.4 → gpt-5.3-codex`). Left as-is; not part of this task's scope.\n- `state/` directory is untracked in repo root (pre-existing).",
