t.`\n- `cargo run -p orbit-cli --bin orbit -- run duel show --root /Users/daniel/workspace/repos/orbit/.orbit` -> `error: invalid input: no duel runs found`\n\n## Design Weaknesses / Risks\n- Workspace build still emits pre-existing dead-code warnings in `orbit-store` and `orbit-engine`; they are unrelated to this fix but still visible during validation.\n",
